  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Safe Water for Families in Rural Ghana</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">As you read this, countless women and children in rural Ghana are walking, searching for water. Children are missing school and women are losing valuable time. Meanwhile, clean water could be right beneath them, deep underground.  The solution? Solar-powered water kiosks that bring clean water to the surface-and provide women and children healthier, happier lives.</narrative>
  </description>
